headline: Why First Interstate BancSystem (FIBK) Stock Is Trading Up Today
summary: Shares of regional banking company First Interstate BancSystem (NASDAQ:FIBK) jumped 3.8% in the afternoon session after positive results from peer regional banks buoyed investor sentiment for the sector.
